{"id":36093,"title":"Sinus pericranii with a hair collar sign.","abstract":"Sinus pericranii is a rare vascular malformation in which the extracranial veins are connected to the intracranial venous circulation. It typically appears as a soft mass with a blue hue on the scalp. We describe a patient with sinus pericranii and associated hair collar sign. ","date":"2014-04-24","categories":"Congenital Hereditary and Neonatal Diseases and Abnormalities","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24602143","annotations":[{"name":"Congenital disorder","weight":0.829843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Congenital_disorder"},{"name":"Vein","weight":0.735569,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vein"},{"name":"Circulatory system","weight":0.664316,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circulatory_system"},{"name":"Hair","weight":0.656612,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hair"},{"name":"Paranasal sinuses","weight":0.41435,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paranasal_sinuses"},{"name":"Vascular","weight":0.360173,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vascular"},{"name":"Scalp","weight":0.217446,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scalp"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.101782,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Blue","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blue"},{"name":"Vascular malformation","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vascular_malformation"},{"name":"Sinus pericranii","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sinus_pericranii"},{"name":"Medical sign","weight":0.0285246,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_sign"},{"name":"Mass","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mass"},{"name":"Hue","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hue"},{"name":"Collar (clothing)"